title: Lonzo's two tallies help Men's Soccer gain critical win over Franciscan (Pitt-Greensburg Athletics)
text: ( Source : Pitt-Greensburg Athletics ) STEUBENVILLE, Ohio : Austin Lonzo ( Greensburg, PA ) had two goals in a must-win match to help propel the Pitt-Greensburg men's soccer team over Franciscan on Wednesday afternoon, 3-1. The Bobcats brought
